{"tid":254409,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基沙文︰6成機會過曼聯","createTime":"2017-05-23T07:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T16:47:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"712b80e5000f538d2e11656b961325f8283d6b8b","tid":254409,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/91/6d/antoine-griezmann-atletico-madrid_yzp4zj3kqfe11fyyd6anvzsv6.jpg?t=-505402317&amp;w=620&amp;h=430\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F91%2F6d%2Fantoine-griezmann-atletico-madrid_yzp4zj3kqfe11fyyd6anvzsv6.jpg%3Ft%3D-505402317%26w%3D620%26h%3D430&h=bff3fdde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬德體育會前鋒基沙文日前接受訪問時表示，將有6成機會在今夏轉會曼聯，並指將在未來兩周作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n預計身價高達8000萬歐元的基沙文，一直盛傳與紅魔扯上關係，亦是領隊摩連奴的心頭好，他日前接受法國電視台訪問時說︰「我將在未來兩星期作出決定。」當被主持問到過檔曼聯的機會，10當中有多少時，他回答︰「6」意味著將有6成機會轉會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然有報道指曼聯能否取得下屆歐聯資格，將是這位法國前鋒轉會與否的關鍵，但據Goal了解即使紅魔未能打入歐聯，亦不影響他的過檔機會。"},{"pid":"2eafff3a52269adac8351f903f90174a9492543f","tid":254409,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee404b3f8d3d1ba7c69c5fc9729ded92e70e890","tid":254409,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:33:52.000Z","msg":"666魔鬼數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4452e7a0e92cc5cfb9c5a02bdf7f5ce2cad4d970","tid":254409,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"All go 曼聯 la diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af58612956c59bda9141d235750cbc4a55c8ff01","tid":254409,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"咁識講野 知我獌鍾意6"},{"pid":"42efc0c48376d0abccc43b61762cd15a99fbc451","tid